DRAWLINE
PRINTW 看着龙神像
PRINTL
PRINTL ……

IF (IS_COLD_LOW && 低气圧位置 != "寒冷涡通过" && DAY:2 != 2) || IS_LINER_RAINBAND:0 == 1 || (IS_SoJ_LOW == 2 && 低气圧位置 != "二つ玉低气圧通过") || CAN_CUMULUS:0 == 5 || CAN_CUMULUS:2 == 2 || CONTINUOUS_RAINFALL >= 20 || POSSIBLITY_AVALANCHE >= 1
